# Deployment Environment Variables

## MongoDB Atlas
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://username:password@cluster0.xxxxx.mongodb.net/campaign-poster-saas?retryWrites=true&w=majority

## Cloudinary (Get from https://cloudinary.com/dashboard)
CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=your_cloud_name_here
CLOUDINARY_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET=your_api_secret_here

## Server Configuration
PORT=5000
NODE_ENV=production

## CORS (Update with your Vercel URL after deployment)
CORS_ORIGIN=https://your-app.vercel.app

## Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env
# 2. Replace placeholder values with your actual credentials
# 3. NEVER commit .env to git (it's in .gitignore)
# 4. Add these variables to Render.com environment variables
